title: Diamond 5 Mid/Top Laner LF Team
body:
Hey guys
I'm looking for a serious team that's aim is to eventually make it into the OCL and eventually OPL. I was Diamond 2 last season and am Diamond 5 now and climbing. I have a very large pool for top and mid since I have been playing since season 2.
I've played on a few high diamond teams in the past such as Enclave Gaming and ELIM Gaming.
If you could comment below or add me in game that would be great.

replies.body: I need a top laner So maybe i could give u a try add me :)
Will do mate just added you!
